Tonight, crazy cop
caps kris kringle.

07:50.838 --> 07:52.188
Brandy Barber reporting.

07:52.732 --> 07:55.465
This city has seen its share
of shocking crimes.

07:55.542 --> 07:57.499
But for the children of San Francisco,

07:57.693 --> 07:59.853
what happened this morning
on that rooftop.

08:00.197 --> 08:02.088
Was the crime
of the century.

08:02.934 --> 08:04.902
The victim,
Michael Kenworthy,

08:05.017 --> 08:08.181
a doting grandfather,
a retired parole officer.

08:08.553 --> 08:09.780
His neighbors call him

08:10.192 --> 08:12.045
the nicest man they ever met.

08:12.227 --> 08:13.312
The facts are these.

08:13.422 --> 08:15.697
Mr. Kenworthy,
in the spirit of christmas,

08:15.876 --> 08:18.403
bought some toys to give away
to the neighborhood children.

08:18.564 --> 08:19.638
He was on that roof

08:19.653 --> 08:23.042
tossing Candy Canes
and stuffed animals down to the street,

08:23.297 --> 08:25.342
when this man,
Adrian Monk,

08:25.739 --> 08:28.170
a disgruntled former homicide detective,

08:28.298 --> 08:31.166
who was kicked off the force
on a psychiatric discharge,

08:31.300 --> 08:33.943
ran up to the roof
and shot Mr. Kenworthy

08:34.265 --> 08:35.441
for no apparent reason.

08:37.722 --> 08:38.808
I'm the grinch.

08:38.828 --> 08:40.260
That's what they're calling me.

08:40.330 --> 08:41.673
The whole city hates me.

08:41.688 --> 08:44.164
I think we're going to be okay.
I've been thinking about this.

08:44.179 --> 08:45.311
It's San Francisco.

08:45.326 --> 08:46.452
It's a godless town.

08:46.467 --> 08:48.284
Everybody knows that.
That's why they visit.

08:48.504 --> 08:50.355
Hippies and heathens despise christmas.

08:50.370 --> 08:52.589
All need is a couple of witches
on the jury, home free.

08:52.604 --> 08:54.769
- That's your strategy?
- That's just the beginning.

08:55.558 --> 08:56.793
How's it going, Randy?

08:57.033 --> 08:58.094
Almost done.

08:58.619 --> 09:02.608
We recovered these on the street
and these were from the toy bag.

09:02.623 --> 09:04.643
We've got 24 dolls,

09:04.658 --> 09:07.226
one rubber snake, five frisbees,
one walkie talkie,

09:07.241 --> 09:09.530
and 37 stuffed animals.

09:09.545 --> 09:11.483
