the bunny or not.

09:11.522 --> 09:13.135
- It's got blood all over it.
- Gray.

09:13.150 --> 09:14.212
Blood on the Bunny.

09:14.264 --> 09:16.340
That's not good.
Most heathens love Bunnies.

09:16.355 --> 09:17.904
I'll have to find one that doesn't.

09:18.710 --> 09:20.087
Okay, finish it later.

09:20.119 --> 09:22.471
All right pal, it's the moment of truth.
Have a seat.

