09:31.928 --> 09:33.462
I am interviewing Adrian Monk.

09:33.754 --> 09:36.539
Garret Price for Mr. Monk
and I have 3:46 pm.

09:37.309 --> 09:38.312
Go.

09:38.622 --> 09:39.885
What happened on the roof?

09:40.762 --> 09:42.588
When I got up there,
that guy.

09:42.603 --> 09:43.604
Santa Claus.

09:43.619 --> 09:45.487
- Mr. Kenworthy.
- Kenworthy.

09:45.727 --> 09:49.103
