He was throwing the toys off the roof.

09:50.762 --> 09:52.017
<i>I asked him to stop.</i>

09:52.446 --> 09:55.354
<i>He told me to leave him alone.
He said my head was made of</i>

09:55.407 --> 09:56.410
<i>B.M.</i>

09:57.434 --> 09:59.395
Right.
Go on.

09:59.434 --> 10:02.205
As I was about to leave,
a gun fell out of his belt.

10:06.499 --> 10:07.630
<i>I asked him about it.</i>

10:07.645 --> 10:09.634
<i>Did he have a permit? He went nuts.</i>

10:11.596 --> 10:13.197
<i>He grab a pipe.</i>

10:13.380 --> 10:14.884
<i>He came at me.</i>

10:18.738 --> 10:20.012
<i>I told him to stop...</i>

10:20.307 --> 10:22.362
<i>Don't.
Don't try it!</i>

10:22.472 --> 10:23.823
<i>He just kept coming.</i>

10:26.937 --> 10:27.959
How many shots?

10:28.572 --> 10:29.575
Two.

10:31.188 --> 10:32.269
And is this the gun?

10:33.269 --> 10:34.272
You're sure?

10:34.311 --> 10:35.820
I remember the broken handle.

10:36.110 --> 10:38.107
Mr. Kenworthy said it's not his gun.

10:38.430 --> 10:41.073
He said that you went nuts
and that you started yelling, cursing.

10:41.528 --> 10:42.948
Then you pulled out this gun.

10:43.049 --> 10:44.168
You started shooting.

10:44.595 --> 10:47.128
- Can you explain that?
- Yes, I can. He's lying.

10:48.169 --> 10:50.347
We got your prints off the weapon,
Monk, not his.

10:50.362 --> 10:51.531
He was wearing gloves.

10:51.863 --> 10:52.924
Santa Claus gloves.

10:53.252 --> 10:54.255
If I may,

10:54.891 --> 10:56.000
what about the bomb?

10:57.701 --> 10:58.704
What bomb?

