11:20.351 --> 11:21.412
There was no bomb.

11:21.450 --> 11:22.820
Why are you protecting him?

11:25.350 --> 11:28.070
May I speak with my client for a moment?
By all means.

11:30.268 --> 11:32.473
First you don't like hippies.
Now you don't like bombs.

11:32.488 --> 11:34.119
Juries love bombs. Just try it out.

11:34.134 --> 11:37.153
Just see how it feels. It was a gun.
Everybody today likes bombs.

11:37.200 --> 11:38.955
No jury will acquit you if
there's a bomb.

11:50.509 --> 11:52.778
Pending further investigation,
we are not certain

11:53.291 --> 11:55.132
