- Look, I have to be sure here.

12:26.050 --> 12:29.599
Do you understand my position here?
It's your word against Santa Claus.

12:29.626 --> 12:31.343
Leland, it was his gun.

12:31.978 --> 12:34.196
It was self defense.

12:34.878 --> 12:37.423
I'll speak to you later today.
Think about the bomb.

12:41.204 --> 12:43.015
