12:45.196 --> 12:47.880
"What do you think, Timmy?
Will christmas ever be the same?"

12:48.952 --> 12:51.287
Maybe they're having nightmares.
Wouldn't that be great?

12:51.350 --> 12:54.209
I thought we were doing that
museum piece. That diamond from Egypt.

12:54.545 --> 12:57.152
We can do the Museum anytime, Jerry.
This is the story.

12:57.480 --> 12:59.179
Cop shoots Santa Claus.

12:59.205 --> 13:00.721
I feel like I won the damn lottery.

13:00.736 --> 13:02.066
