13:03.361 --> 13:05.414
He said it's about that cop,
Adrian Monk.

13:12.552 --> 13:14.230
- Brandy Barber.
- How you doing?

13:14.536 --> 13:17.401
- I saw your story tonight on the news.
- Great, thanks for watching.

13:17.416 --> 13:19.172
<i>Anyway,
I thought you might be interested.</i>

13:19.187 --> 13:21.135
<i>I live near that crazy cop Monk,</i>

13:21.370 --> 13:22.624
