13:25.830 --> 13:27.412
Yes, sir. It's a real shame.

13:27.460 --> 13:28.618
What can I do for you?

13:28.701 --> 13:29.790
I just saw him.

13:30.042 --> 13:31.054
Monk.

13:31.190 --> 13:32.968
He was in the yard behind our building.

13:33.754 --> 13:35.056
I could tell he was nervous.

13:35.071 --> 13:36.192
He was pacing around.

13:36.306 --> 13:37.327
He had a shovel.

13:37.495 --> 13:38.498
Shovel?

13:39.988 --> 13:41.461
That's Monk's building.

13:41.504 --> 13:43.799
The guy said at the blue doorway

13:44.166 --> 13:45.478
go 20 feet to the right.

13:48.544 --> 13:49.818
In front of the bench.

13:49.987 --> 13:51.627
